e, and vitality.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aMusicxReligious aspects. 0aMusiczMexicozMexico CityxHistory and criticism. 0aRites and ceremonieszMexicozMexico City. 7aMUSIC / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Texas Press eBook-Package Backlist 2000-2013z978311074534440uhttps://doi.org/10.7560/70231840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780292798489423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780292798489/original  a978-3-11-074534-4  University of Texas Press eBook-Package Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MUAR  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK